title: Shake Your Moneymaker
description: Live richer, and save your energy and time for all those things you want to do in your life. How? "Shake Your Moneymaker" gives you the secret tool, through the five steps of Maria Bunyemens Golden Prosperity Model.This eBook on Economy & Leadership is written for you, no matter how your life situations look like and no matter where you want to head in life. Maria Bunyemens 5 powerful steps will lead you to start leading yourself.Her 5 steps will help you move in both new & familiar ways, surprising yourself of your own capacities. Find out today what these 5 steps are, and how you can make them work for you!Invest in yourself. Get richer, and save both your time and energy by doing things the right way, your way!Get it and start living your life the way you dream of.shakeyourmoneymaker.se
author: Maria Bunyemen
